<style type="text/css">
  body {
    font-family: "Arial", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    font-size: 8px;
    line-height: 1em;
  }

  .container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    margin: 0 0.76cm;
  }

  /*
   * Header
   */

  .pdf-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 0.25cm;
    padding-bottom: 0px;
    border-bottom: 3px solid #05373c;
  }

  .pdf-header-title {
    flex: 1 auto;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #05373c;
    line-height: 1em;
    height: 1em;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
  }

  .pdf-header-logo {
    flex: 200px 0 auto;
    margin-left: 10px;
  }

  /*
   * Footer
   */

  .pdf-footer {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 0.2cm;
  }

  .pdf-footer p {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .pdf-footer p + p {
    margin-top: 0.3em;
  }

  .pdf-footer-content {
    flex: 1 auto;
  }

  .pdf-footer-upsell img {
    vertical-align: middle;
  }

  .pdf-footer-upsell span {
    position: relative;
    top: 2px;
  }

  .pdf-footer-pages {
    flex: 0 auto;
    margin-top: auto;
  }
</style>
